dc_description_s: This data represents general zoning for Burnett County, Wisconsin in 2022. [The shapefile contains zoning information for townships in Burnett County that are zoned. It should be noted that even if a township has not adopted a zoning policy, land nearby watercourses in Burnett County is zoned. For more information on township zoning, please contact the Burnett County Land Use Office.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
